snippet.title: Ominous Canyon - Part I
snippet.description:
Science Ming was studying and working with the monsters he found in Ominous Canyon, when an experiment went terribly wrong. What will happen next?
Ominous Canyon is only the 1st chapter on this new adventure and more will come in the future!

Fiesta Online is a Free2Play Anime MMORPG with an active Community and lots of exciting Adventures!

Look forward for the new upcoming content!
